block.comment: Parsons Problem - Make it so when the sprite is clicked, if it is a hospital, it becomes an ambulance and vice versa.
Buggy Code - Debug the code so that If the sprite is an ambulance, it moves and if number of treatments is less than 0, "are treatments available" becomes false.
When space key is pressed, reset the stage.

Add Mortality After a Person has been infected for more than 7 days, If the person hasBeenTreated, they should switch their costume to healthy! If they haven't been treated, they should die. Use the blocks to the right to add mortaility to this part of the script.
